00:12:01.879 --> 00:12:03.349
Also, the World Values Survey,

00:12:03.373 --> 00:12:05.682
which surveys countries
from all over the world

00:12:05.706 --> 00:12:08.617
and has been doing so since the early 80s,

00:12:08.641 --> 00:12:13.543
has found that a composite of what
we might think of as liberal values,

00:12:13.567 --> 00:12:17.068
that composite still shows huge
differences among the world's regions.

00:12:17.092 --> 00:12:20.298
Like, Western Europe is certainly
more liberal than the Middle East.

00:12:20.322 --> 00:12:24.326
But all of them have increased
over the last 50 years.

00:12:24.350 --> 00:12:28.093
CA: But one problem
of saying this to some people

